## 🚀 Features

- 📂 Upload PDF or TXT files  
- 🔍 Extract and process document content  
- 🧠 Generate embeddings using OpenAI  
- 📦 Store vectors using FAISS  
- 💬 Ask questions and get context-aware answers  
- 🖥️ Interactive UI using Gradio  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python  
- LangChain  
- OpenAI API  
- FAISS (Vector Database)  
- Gradio  

---

## ⚙️ How It Works

1. User uploads a document (PDF/TXT)  
2. Document is split into smaller chunks  
3. Each chunk is converted into embeddings  
4. Embeddings are stored in FAISS vector database  
5. User asks a question  
6. Relevant chunks are retrieved  
7. LLM generates answer based only on retrieved context  

